#~ msgid ""
#~ "[DEPRECATED: Prefer exchangerates_apilayer.com]. You can get the list of "
#~ "available quotes from <a href=\"https://exchangeratesapi.io/"
#~ "\">exchangeratesapi.io</a>.<br/><br/>Then, you must create an account to "
#~ "get an API key and set it in setting.<br/>Then, enter the expected quote "
#~ "in expected currency. Example: if you want BTC in USD, you must enter BTC-"
#~ "USD."
